Saragossa — a pure-Rust Metal LLM inference engine.

This project's Metal compute kernels (src/kernels.metal) implement quantized
matmul / attention algorithms that are conceptually derived from Apple's MLX
(https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx), which is distributed under the MIT License
(Copyright © 2023 Apple Inc.). The kernels here are an independent Rust/Metal
reimplementation (distinct naming and structure); no source was copied verbatim.
We gratefully acknowledge the MLX project.
